text: Louiza Patikas (born 1976 or 1977) is a British actress, known for her roles as Helen Titchener in the BBC Radio 4 soap opera The Archers and Moira Pollock on the ITV soap opera Coronation Street from 2017 to 2020. == Other websites == * Category:1970s births Category:Living people Category:British radio actors Category:British television actors Category:English journalists Category:Actors from Surrey
